<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
    <style type="text/css">
        table {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;margin:0;}
        div, td {padding:0;}
        div {margin:0 !important;}
    </style>
    <noscript>
    <xml>
        <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
        </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
    </xml>
    </noscript>
    <![endif]-->
  </head>
  <body
    style='margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f6f6f6;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#333333;'
  >
    <table
      role='presentation'
      cellpadding='0'
      cellspacing='0'
      width='100%'
      style='border-collapse:collapse;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td align='center' style='padding:40px 0;'>
          <table
            role='presentation'
            cellpadding='0'
            cellspacing='0'
            width='600'
            style='border-collapse:collapse;max-width:600px;background-color:#ffffff;box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);'
          >
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td align='left' style='padding:30px;'>
                <img
                  src='https://i.imgur.com/SuhBLRR.png'
                  alt='LinguaHub Logo'
                  width='150'
                  style='display:block;max-width:200px;height:auto;'
                />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding:0px 30px;'>

                <p>Dear <strong>{{translatorName}}</strong>,</p>

                <p>We hope this email finds you well. We have carefully reviewed
                  your application to join our platform as a translator.</p>

                <p>After thorough consideration, we are pleased to inform you
                  that we have
                  <span
                    style='font-weight:bold;text-decoration: underline;'
                  >{{status}}</span>
                  your application.</p>

                {{#if isApproved}}
                  <p
                    style='background-color:#e8f6fe;padding:15px;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;'
                  ><strong>Congratulations on becoming a part of our esteemed
                      translation team!</strong></p>
                  <p>We are excited to welcome you aboard and look forward to a
                    fruitful collaboration. To get started, please follow these
                    steps:</p>
                  <ol
                    style='background-color:#f9f9f9;padding:20px 20px 20px 40px;border-radius:5px;'
                  >
                    <li><strong style='color:#2563eb;'>Access Your Dashboard:</strong>
                      Log into your personalized translator dashboard to start
                      receiving translation requests and manage your profile.</li>
                    <li><strong style='color:#2563eb;'>Complete Your Profile:</strong>
                      Ensure your profile is comprehensive, showcasing your
                      expertise, portfolio, and service offerings.</li>
                    <li><strong style='color:#2563eb;'>Set Your Services:</strong>
                      Set your service with the language and price you prefer.</li>
                    <li><strong style='color:#2563eb;'>Review Our Guidelines:</strong>
                      Familiarize yourself with our translation standards and
                      best practices.</li>
                  </ol>
                  <p>We are confident that your skills and expertise will be
                    valuable assets to our platform and clients.</p>
                  <p style='text-align:center;margin-top:30px;'>
                    <a
                      href='https://linguahub.com/login'
                      style='background-color:#2563eb;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 20px;border-radius:5px;font-weight:bold;'
                    >Access Your Dashboard</a>
                  </p>
                {{else}}
                  <p
                    style='background-color:#fff1f2;padding:15px;border-left:4px solid #e11d48;'
                  >We appreciate your interest in joining our platform. After
                    careful consideration, we regret to inform you that we are
                    unable to approve your application at this time.</p>
                  {{#if reason}}
                    <p><strong style='text-decoration:underline;'>Reason for
                        Decision:</strong>
                      {{reason}}</p>
                  {{/if}}
                  <p>We encourage you to continue developing your skills and
                    experience. You are welcome to reapply in the future as your
                    qualifications evolve.</p>
                {{/if}}

                <p
                  style='border-top:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-bottom:1px solid #e0e0e0;padding:15px 0;margin-top:30px;'
                >If you have any questions or need further clarification, please
                  don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at
                  <a
                    href='mailto:support@linguahub.com'
                    style='color:#2563eb;text-decoration:underline;'
                  >support@linguahub.com</a>.</p>

                <p>We appreciate your interest in LinguaHub and wish you success
                  in your professional endeavors.</p>

                <p>Best regards,<br /><strong style='color:#2c3e50;'>The
                    LinguaHub Team</strong></p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td
                align='center'
                bgcolor='#172554'
                style='padding:20px;color:#f9fafb;font-size:14px;'
              >
                <p style='margin:0;'>&copy; 2024 LinguaHub. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p style='margin:10px 0 0;'>
                  <a
                    href='#'
                    style='color:#f9fafb;text-decoration:underline;'
                  >Privacy Policy</a>
                  |
                  <a
                    href='#'
                    style='color:#f9fafb;text-decoration:underline;'
                  >Terms of Service</a>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>